Program: Outlook
Title: Outlook in Delhi
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00m1c65
Last Broadcast Date: Tue 13 Dec 2011
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. All of this week Outlook is broadcasting from the Indian capital Delhi. One hundred years since the city became the capital of modern India, Matthew Bannister hears from some of the extraordinary people who live there. Today, he meets 101 year old Changezi Khan. Born and raised in Delhi, he describes the changes he has seen over the past century. Show less